{"tid":1887742,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"講左兩日，究竟LMK藍既證據係邊???","createTime":"2020-02-19T18:05:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T04:48:18.000Z","uid":58335,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e888c8a6bceade7fd33c2179739a35b5f3ca4247","tid":1887742,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T18:05:28.000Z","msg":"我見有好多人話佢串話佢唔識做人上莊又點點點<br />\n但關佢係藍咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪我Miss左睇唔到?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n等左兩日，D所謂證據都見唔到<br />\n開po條友咩po都冇出過就比人帶風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兒登仔就信到十足<br />\n唔比佢係KOL100??<br />\n你話佢左膠都ok，但有冇證據指出佢點藍法??<br />\n咁我聽日又出過po話天琦哥係藍屍先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n定係學689適時考慮披露外國勢力介入證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:非fans&amp;打手，你地睇唔睇都唔關我事，不過係以事論事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20141105/s00001/1415172875225SL4_A6630C401D324943106AD1BCB0CB0821.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20141105%2Fs00001%2F1415172875225SL4_A6630C401D324943106AD1BCB0CB0821.jpg&h=e7ea451d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24beb41b26a43640573934e8b2aac2d9c88164a6","tid":1887742,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T18:08:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daee6f0e72cb17152973bcec3c04f061c686ad63","tid":1887742,"uid":177213,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T18:08:19.000Z","msg":"淨係冇表態+扮中立+反鶳已經唔係手足啦"},{"pid":"f3cf59b104a826e080a3a611fa01306c0df0291a","tid":1887742,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T18:08:43.000Z","msg":"當香港人仲掛住排口罩 搶廁紙 討論邊個邊個ig女神<br />\n<a href=\"https: